{"tid":2030904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"金牛座tg谷-唔想入谷就去post到吹","createTime":"2020-05-23T05:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T04:20:33.000Z","uid":217514,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"953b364bd59a4b5262e8e6b7748042e598e03261","tid":2030904,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"大家好 金牛jj嚟圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我地係有連登post一齊圍爐<br />\n但知道唔係人人想係post到傾/有ac<br />\n所以開多個tg谷 可以入谷圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎曾經入過嘅無限再入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但發現入過嘅係唔會加得返 所以張form都麻煩你備注返<br />\n會有專人另外搵你</span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎非金牛座嘅人入 一齊為你解決溝金牛仔/女嘅難題<br />\n又或者友情上都可以 唔一定要愛情<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但絕對唔歡迎入嚟純交友 sorry 呢到唔係搵食谷 活動台大把吹水谷比你入<br />\n</span><br />\n請記住 未加前都盡量唔好轉tg id，私隱都較返公開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTg私穩冇較到比任何人加入谷，我係唔會特登Pm你再去加。（你可以係tg設定》私隱同保安〉谷同台》所有人<br />\n<br />\nTg user id:如何設定user id, 設定》編輯個人資料〉用戶名<br />\n<br />\n最後 潛水3日就踢 所以會維持係3日加一次人<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/YKWbL9DVft2VFTNF6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYKWbL9DVft2VFTNF6&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=b55e9c94\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/YKWbL9DVft2VFTNF6</a>"},{"pid":"1e339a3603f8b23ed78b5800a78f2980fb1a7f30","tid":2030904,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4df6206888080c67590b802a957ebd7af431f4","tid":2030904,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg